Name: Strike Force: Arctic Storm
About the game: Strike Force: Arctic Storm is a small First-Person-Shooter game in the style of old, classic Delta Force games and a standalone add-on for Strike Force: Desert Thunder. You join 5 intense, large scale missions to prevent terrorist attacks. Customize your loadout, choose between 14 weapons and jump right into the action. Each Mission is large scale (2kmÂ²) and open to your tactical strategy. Develop your own plan to attack the terrorists!
